 <%-include ("../layouts/header") %>
 <main>
   <section class="section-about">
     <div class=" container">
       <div class="col-12">
         <div class="row">
           <div class="col-md-6 mx-auto">
             <h2 class="section-about__heading">
               We Are The Best In The Business
             </h2>
           </div>
           <div class="row">
             <div class="col-md-6">
               <h3 class="section-about__subheading">
                 Our Story
               </h3>
               <p class="section-about__text">
                 Founded in 2023, Dreams Events was born out of a passion for creating extraordinary experiences and unforgettable moments. Our mission is to deliver exceptional event planning services and unparalleled customer satisfaction.

                 Why Dreams Events? Because we believe in the power of dreams. Whether it's an intimate gathering or a grand affair, we are dedicated to crafting unique events that leave a lasting impression on your guests. We take pride in offering personalized touches, ensuring that every detail, from the layout to the drink selection and exquisite decor, reflects your distinct vision</p>
               <h3 class="section-about__subheading">

                 <h3> Our Vision </h3>
                 <p class="section-about__text">
                   At Dreams Events, we understand that your event is an expression of your dreams and aspirations. Our team of skilled professionals will work closely with you to bring your vision to life, transforming your ideas into a remarkable reality. From conceptualization to execution, we are committed to going above and beyond to create an event that surpasses your expectations.

                   With Dreams Events, the possibilities are limitless. We embrace creativity and innovation, constantly seeking fresh ideas and trends to elevate your event to new heights. Whether it's a corporate gathering, a wedding celebration, or any other special occasion, we strive to make it an extraordinary and unforgettable experience for both you and your guests.

                   Dream big and let us turn your dreams into reality. Contact Dreams Events today and let us embark on a journey together to create an event that will be cherished for years to come.
                 </p>
                </div>
               <hr>
               <div class="col-md-6 container">
                 <div class="thumbnail">
                   <img src="../images/ibrahim-boran-m8YjB0noWiY-unsplash.jpg" class="rounded mx-auto d-block" alt="Photo 1">
                   <hr>
                   <img src="../images/billy-huynh-saS98jKhVjA-unsplash.jpg" class="rounded mx-auto d-block" alt="Photo 2">
                 </div>
               </div>
             </div>
             <div class="caption ">
               <h4>Checkout our blogs:</h4>
             </div>
             <div class="thumbnail row">
               <% if (blogs.length > 0) { %>
               <% blogs.forEach(function(blog) { %>
               <div class="blog col-md-4">
                 <a href="/blogs/" class="text-decoration-none thumbnail-link">
                   <div class="about-page-blog-multimedia">
                     <% if (blog.multimedia.type === 'video') { %>
                     <iframe src="<%= blog.multimedia.url %>" frameborder="0"></iframe>
                     <% } else if (blog.multimedia.type === 'image') { %>
                     <img src="../../images/<%= blog.multimedia.url %>" alt="<%= blog.multimedia.description %>">
                     <% } else if (blog.multimedia.type === 'audio') { %>
                     <audio src="<%= blog.multimedia.url %>" controls></audio>
                     <% } else if (blog.multimedia.type === 'interactive') { %>
                     <iframe src="<%= blog.multimedia.url %>" frameborder="0"></iframe>
                     <% } %>
                   </div>
                   <p class="about-page-blog-content"><%= blog.content %></p>
                 </a>
               </div>
               <% }); %>
               <% } else { %>
               <p>Trying to load our blog post, stay jiggy.</p>
               <% } %>
             </div>
           </div>
         </div>
       </div>
       <hr>
   </section>
 </main>
<hr>
 <footer>
   <%- include("../layouts/footer") %>
 </footer>